Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}黄昏交差点　駆け寄る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}“会いたい”と思う　そんな気持ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}空を泳いでる　雲みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}ぶつかって　溶けて　消えた？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}いつからだろう　すれ違ってる…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}それでも　とこかで　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}あなただけ　求めて…いる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}会いたくて…　青空（そら）に描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}未来へと　続く　願い…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}今日もまた　こんなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}眩しくて…　愛しくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}陽だまりに並んで咲いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}向日葵みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}見つめてたい　キラキラ　My Love
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}奔向黃昏時分的十字路口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}想見你的心情就好像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}天空中飄浮的雲朵一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}互相碰撞 溶化 消失而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}也不知從何時開始 我們彼此錯過對方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}即便如此我也會在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}尋求著唯一的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}在藍天畫下了"想見你"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}期盼一直到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}今天也是那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}讓人眩暈 讓人憐愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}猶如向日葵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}和陽光一起競相開放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}凝望著耀眼的　My Love
